----
== YAML Misconceptions

* YAML was created to improve JSON
* YAML is a config language
* YAML was forced on DevOps
* Kubernetes made YAML popular
* YAML is a superset of JSON
* YAML frameworks follow the spec
* YAML is finished
* Norway is a problem


----
== YAML has Problems

* YAML is critical infrastructure with massive usage
* No two YAML frameworks behave the same
* None passed the YAML 1.2 spec test suite until 2021

* These problems can be fixed
* Ingy is dedicated to fixing YAML's problems
  * And moving the language forward for everybody
  * Many improvements are already underway
* YAML needs corporate sponsorship to thrive


----
